edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i. AS Roma v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Barcelona \u0111ang \u201cv\u00e0o phom\u201d. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khi r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch mang t\u00ednh an \u1ee7i c\u1ee7a Edin Dzeko.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Roma c\u00f2n h\u00e0o ph\u00f3ng t\u1eb7ng cho Barca 2 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Daniele De Rossi v\u00e0 Kostas Manolas b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Gerard Pique. \u00dd \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a HLV Eusebio Di Francesco l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng: T\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tran dau Roma vs Barca (1h45 ngay 114) No nan chong chat hinh anh\" title=\"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca (1h45 ng\u00e0y 114) N\u1ee3 n\u1ea7n ch\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Tran-dau-Roma-vs-Barca-(1h45-ngay-114)-No-nan-chong-chat-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 \u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca. C\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t 3 b\u00e0n gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Roma v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n. Thay v\u00ec d\u00f9ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Barca, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Di Francesco gi\u1edd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u Roma mu\u1ed1n m\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf bu\u1ed9c h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 d\u0129 nhi\u00ean, Barca c\u1ee7a Ernesto Valverde r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV 54 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia t\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ea7y bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 ch\u01a1i trong th\u1ebf \u201cc\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Barca. \u0110\u00f4i khi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ea3 9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Blaugrana ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Lionel Messi \u0111\u1ec1u tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n 2 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Suarez va Messi tai Barca\" title=\"Suarez va Messi tai Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/5/Suarez-va-Messi-tai-Barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Suarez v\u00e0 Messi v\u1eabn \u0111ang gi\u00fap Blaugrana bay cao</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i La Liga, Barca m\u1edbi n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi nh\u00f3m b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 11 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc 7 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u1ea1i c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua, h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Sevilla \u0111\u00eam 21/4 t\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i Champions League, d\u00f9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca ch\u01b0a di\u1ec5n ra, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 coi Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leganes. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c. T\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp cho t\u1edbi 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-leganes-01h45-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183740.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ket-qua-barca-vs-leganes-tran-dau-vong-31-la-liga-201718.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-barca-vs-leganes-01h45-ngay-84-la-liga-201718-372-183740.html\">Barca 3-1 Leganes (KT): C\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a Messilona</span><br>\r\n<span>Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu Leganes, Barcelona d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 nh\u1edd c\u00fa hattrick c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi. V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Messi v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9, c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Roma v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Giallorossi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 b\u00e0n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Roma ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo k\u00e8m Messi. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi \u201csi\u00eau nh\u00e2n\u201d ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, m\u1ed9t r\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Hu\u1ed1ng chi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn m\u1ea5t m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t Radja Nainggolan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u01b0a l\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Roma vs Barcelona\" title=\"Preview Roma vs Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Preview-Roma-vs-Barcelona.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca 1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd: Roma ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 3 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Olimpico, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Roma s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thua c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Barca nh\u01b0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ea7n k\u1ef3 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m trong t\u00e2m tr\u00ed c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u00e1o b\u00e3 tr\u1ea7u. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nRoma (4-3-3):</strong> 1.Alisson - 24.Florenzi, 44.Manolas, 20.Fazio, 11.Kolarov - 3.Pellegrini, 16.De Rossi, 6.Strootman - 17.Under, 9.Dzeko, 8.Perotti.<br>\r\n<strong>Barca (4-4-2): </strong>1.Stegen - 2.Semedo, 3.Pique, 23.Umtiti, 18.Alba - 20.Roberto, 15.Paulinho, 4.Rakitic, 8.Iniesta - 10.Messi, 9.Suarez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: Barca th\u1eafng 2-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Roma vs Barca\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Roma vs Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Roma-vs-Barcelona-(4-3-3-vs-4-4-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Roma vs Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Barcelona tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chao-gia-soc-cho-hau-ve-vo-danh-180-183910.html\">Barca ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 s\u1ed1c cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 v\u00f4 danh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-bao-gio-messi-thanh-liet-si-cua-barca-180-183894.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Bao gi\u1edd Messi th\u00e0nh \u201cli\u1ec7t s\u0129\u201d c\u1ee7a Barca?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-nhan-barca-khong-co-le-don-tan-vuong-nao-ca-180-183842.html\">Sergio Ramos nh\u1eafn Barca: Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ec5 \u0111\u00f3n t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0o c\u1ea3</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-don-tin-vui-truoc-them-tu-ket-luot-ve-champions-league-184-183824.html\">Barca \u0111\u00f3n tin vui tr\u01b0\