argin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jan Oblak r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovenia.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jan Oblak \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/jan-oblak-44472.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Jan Oblak </strong></span>n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovenia \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, anh c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 doi bong chi 100 trieu euro dua Jan Oblak roi Atletico Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0a Jan Oblak r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/29/3-doi-bong-chi-100-trieu-euro-dua-Jan-Oblak-roi-Atletico-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jan Oblak \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Atletico Madrid, anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n sau 31 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf La Liga.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Oblak l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Atletico s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t La Liga sau 31 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Atetico kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd gi\u1eef Oblak tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Oblak</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jan Oblak r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Slovenia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 doi bong chi 100 trieu euro dua Jan Oblak roi Atletico Madrid hinh anh\" title=\"3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0a Jan Oblak r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/3-doi-bong-chi-100-trieu-euro-mua-thu-mon-atletico-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u01b0a Jan Oblak r\u1eddi Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/xac-nhan-mu-hoi-mua-sao-khung-cua-atletico-madrid-172-159816.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>M.U quan t\u00e2m Oblak</strong></span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p David de Gea ra \u0111i. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, vi\u1ec7c De Gea lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u1ebfu anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 thay Thibaut Courtois. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid quan t\u00e2m.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6 n\u0103m 2019, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb\u00a0ch\u1ed1i. C\u00f3 tin cho r\u1eb1ng anh \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Alphonse Areola ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00f2n vai v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf Champions League h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro, vi\u1ec7c Jan Oblak r\u1eddi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/atletico-madrid-1390.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Atletico Madrid</strong></span> c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jan Oblak \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/69768-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Jan Oblak \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"976","checkdouble":"183917"},{"date":"07:46 10/04","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh N\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs N\u1eef Australia 00h00 ng\u00e0y 11/4 (VCK ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/nhan-dinh-nu-viet-nam-vs-nu-australia-00h00-ngay-114-vck-chau-a-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:My