m,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/4.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Barca ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho trung v\u1ec7 v\u00f4 danh. </strong>Theo Telefoot, Barcelona \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00e0o gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tu\u1ed5i teen Dayot Upamecano c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Upamecano \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 6 Bundesliga v\u00e0 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Europa League. Trung v\u1ec7 19 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft Man United, Bayern Munich, Arsenal r\u1ed3i AC Milan quan t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Man United.</strong> Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marcus Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Manchester United v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Rashford \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 43 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 22 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. M\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin th\u00e2n c\u1eadn cho hay vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u1edf derby Manchester cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua khi\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 20 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem tin bong da sang ngay 104 Rashford co the roi Man United hinh anh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 104 Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Rashford-co-the-roi-MU.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rashford c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Juventus mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Morata. </strong>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Mundo Deportivo, Juventus\u00a0 \u0111ang t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alvaro Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Morata t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i cho Juventus d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2016 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real Madrid mua l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao tr\u1ebb Barca.</strong> Arsenal \u0111ang d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho sao tr\u1ebb Robert Navarro c\u1ee7a Barcelona. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7, Man City c\u0169ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi m\u0169i c\u00f4ng m\u1edbi 15 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c n\u00e0o. Navarro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 do r\u1eddi Barca khi b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 16 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 5 t\u1edbi (12/4) trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>3 CLB s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Oblak. </strong>T\u1edd Don Balon cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u1ecf kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jan Oblak v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid. Paris Saint-Germain l\u00e0 1 khi c\u1ea7n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh. Chelsea v\u00e0 Man United l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i khi n\u01a1m n\u1edbp lo s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t \u0111i nh\u1eefng Thibaut Courtois v\u00e0 David de Gea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Oblak\" title=\"Oblak\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/6/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-1401-Sanchez-da-o-rat-gan-MU-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Oblak nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Torres ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u1ea1i Atletico. </strong>Fernando Torres m\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Atletico Madrid v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2017/18. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u1ed9t n\u01a1i kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Salah tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn Man City. </strong>Ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Man City t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 Champions League, Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t tin c\u1ef1c vui. Ng\u00f4i sao Mohamed Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 Man xanh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Etihad.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"974","checkdouble":"183913"},{"date":"07:58 10/04","title":"Man City vs Liverpool (1h45 ng\u00e0y 11/4): C\u00f2n n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n t\u00e1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/10/man-city-vs-liverpool-1h45-ngay-114-con-nuoc-con-tat.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;lef