ri\u1ec7u Euro. L\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t ti\u1ebft h\u1ebft t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i khi ngo\u00e0i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i, Upamecano \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bundesliga m\u00f9a 2017/18. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Telefoot \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Barcelona \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i cho m\u1ecdi l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb U16 cho t\u1edbi U21 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca mua trung ve Upamecano voi gia 100 trieu Euro hinh anh\" title=\"Barca mua trung v\u1ec7 Upamecano v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/10/Dayot--Upamecano-cua-RB-Leipzig.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mua trung v\u1ec7 Upamecano v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 s\u1ed1c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nUpamecano c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi RB Leipzig \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 t\u1edbi Champions League. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH Bundesliga v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 4 l\u00e0 Leverkusen. Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng B\u1eafc n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1eeb Upamecano.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Barca nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Upamecano. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Gerard Pique \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 31. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Barca mua trung v\u1ec7 Upamecano v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal chung cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Upamecano ch\u1ec9 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t 5 tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i Bundesliga cho RB Leipzig t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 anh, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u1ee9c thua t\u1edbi 3, h\u00f2a 1 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p v\u1edbi CLB \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jose Mourinho tiet lo y do chien thuat tran MU vs Swansea.\" title=\"HLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt tr\u1eadn MU vs Swansea.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/31/mourinho-chi-102-trieu-bang-nang-cap-hang-thu-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Mourinho c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Upamecano</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Barca, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i gia kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Bayern Munich, Manchester United, Arsenal v\u00e0 AC Milan c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho Upamecano \u00e1nh m\u1eaft th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1ng 10 n\u0103m 1998 l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao h\u01a1n. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c. \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Leipzig. Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-dang-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-mu-180-183720.html\">Barca \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-munich-tinh-gay-soc-voi-thu-mon-cua-barca-193-183713.html\">Bayern Munich t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-barca-khong-mua-verratti-180-183658.html\">Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/coutinho-muon-barca-mua-salah-180-183622.html\">Coutinho mu\u1ed1n Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 si\u00eau sao n\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ed3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/umtiti-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-griezmann-180-183457.html\">Umtiti n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Griezmann?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-da-tim-duoc-nguoi-thay-the-umtiti-180-183456.html\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Umtiti</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"972","checkdouble":"183910"},{"date":"08:29 10/04","title":"Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/2/9/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;pad