annel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb Mundo Deportivo, k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch Juventus mua Alvaro Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua. Bianconeri r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng c\u00f3 2 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Turin t\u1eeb 2014 \u0111\u1ebfn 2016.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Morata \u0111ang kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n sang Chelsea t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Alvaro Morata \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh ban \u0111\u1ea7u c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i Chelsea, Morata th\u1ecfa \u01b0\u1edbc nguy\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Karim Benzema nh\u01b0 \u1edf Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Morata, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea c\u00e0ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng b\u00e2y nhi\u00eau v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c khi\u1ebfn cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi. Con s\u1ed1 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 41 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Morata l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u00edt \u1ecfi ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb anh b\u1ecf l\u1ee1.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Alvaro Morata cua Chelsea hinh anh\" title=\"Juventus mua Alvaro Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/9/juventus-mua-alvaro-morata-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus mua Alvaro Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Morata</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Morata t\u1eebng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Bianconeri t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2014 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2016 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real mua l\u1ea1i theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Juventus \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t Paulo Dybala tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay c\u1ea3 khi gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina, \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d v\u1eabn c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 Morata l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-dybala-o-he-2018-176-182547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/12/26/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-dybala-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/lo-ben-do-cuc-soc-cua-dybala-o-he-2018-176-182547.html\">L\u1ed9 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 c\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Dybala \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Dybala t\u1edbi Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Alvaro Morata l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u1ee3p. Ni\u1ec1m tin m\u00e0 Chelsea d\u00e0nh cho Morata \u0111ang xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p c\u00f2n HLV Antonio Conte, ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge c\u1ee7a anh th\u00ec t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Morata, Juventus c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Neymar v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tin s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i ngay trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-juventus-len-tieng-ve-chuyen-chieu-mo-sao-liverpool-172-183896.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/man-city-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-isco-176-183878.html\">Man City c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 Isco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chi-110-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-coutinho-172-183803.html\">Liverpool chi 110 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Coutinho?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-mua-paulo-dybala-cung-real-va-mu-180-182875.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn tranh \u201cti\u1ec3u Messi\u201d c\u00f9ng Real v\u00e0 M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/martial-muon-dao-tau-khoi-mu-172-182219.html\">Ch\u00e1n c\u1ea3nh d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Martial mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Seria A</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"971","checkdouble":"183915"},{"date":"14:48 09/04","title":"C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/cuu-cau-thu-vleague-bi-bat-vi-lua-dao.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity