none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eb1ng Tcheuko Minh, t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1 cho Ki\u00ean Giang, \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed3ng Nai, b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng an C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 b\u1eaft gi\u1eef v\u00ec t\u1ed9i l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ebfm \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eb1ng Tcheuko Minh (35 tu\u1ed5i, qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam) b\u1ecb b\u1eaft gi\u1eef c\u00f9ng Monthe De Fouda Paul Martial (29 tu\u1ed5i, Cameroon) v\u00e0 Ifeanyi Matthew Anthony (28 tu\u1ed5i, Nigeria).\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuu cau thu V-League bi bat vi lua dao phu nu hinh anh\" title=\"C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League b\u1ecb b\u1eaft v\u00ec l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/addsa-9849-1523258429.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eb1ng Tcheuko Minh trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110\u1ed3ng Nai thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf V-League 2015. \u1ea2nh: \u0110\u1ee9c \u0110\u1ed3ng/Vnexpress.net</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo c\u01a1 quan \u0111i\u1ec1u tra, cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m 2016, nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ebfm \u0111o\u1ea1t t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n v\u1edbi chi\u00eau th\u1ee9c l\u00e0m quen ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam qua m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u1eb7ng qu\u00e0 cho h\u1ecd r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm \u0111o\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e1ng 2/2018, Papa cung c\u1ea5p cho Anthony th\u00f4ng tin \"ng\u01b0\u1eddi quen\" l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u1edf ph\u01b0\u1eddng H\u01b0ng L\u1ee3i, qu\u1eadn Ninh Ki\u1ec1u, C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1. Ng\u00e0y 22/3, Minh \u0111\u00f3ng vai l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ty chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y n\u00f3i c\u00f3 th\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 \u1edf M\u1ef9 g\u1eedi v\u1ec1, y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00f3ng ph\u00ed h\u1ea3i quan 1.600 \u0111\u00f4la. Tin l\u1eddi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng n\u1ed9p ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00f3m l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o vi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c moi ti\u1ec1n n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n. Khi th\u00ec n\u00f3i h\u1ea3i quan g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, khi l\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam dung d\u1ecbch h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \"r\u1eeda\" nh\u1eefng c\u1ecdc gi\u1ea5y tr\u1eafng trong th\u00f9ng h\u00e0ng ra ti\u1ec1n th\u1eadt... T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng Minh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u1ea1m \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eeba l\u1ea5y h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng an C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec1u tra m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng v\u1ee5 \u00e1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eb1ng Tcheuko Minh t\u00ean th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Benoit Tcheuko, sinh n\u0103m 1983 t\u1ea1i Cameroon. Sau khi \u0111\u1ebfn V-League, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Ki\u00ean Giang, \u0110\u1ed3ng Th\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed3ng Nai. Ng\u00e0y 23/4/2013, Tcheuko \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eadp t\u1ecbch b\u1eb1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u1ee3 l\u00e0 ngu\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 sau khi ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng th\u00ec tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \"c\u00f2\" c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Vnexpress.net<br>\r\n</em></div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"970","checkdouble":"183880"},{"date":"15:01 09/04","title":"Nghi \u00e1n sao MU c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh kh\u1ea1c nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a Man City","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/nghi-an-sao-mu-co-tinh-khac-nho-vao-logo-cua-man-city.png","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type