lor:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ander Herrera g\u00e2y ra tranh c\u00e3i khi c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn derby th\u00e0nh Manchester h\u00f4m 8/4.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCamera ghi l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ng\u00f4i sao MU\u00a0ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f3 v\u1ebb l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1ea1c nh\u1ed5, tr\u00fang logo c\u1ee7a Man City khi \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ea7m gi\u1eefa hai hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u khi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 2-0 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Man xanh. Herrera \u0111i sau hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 Gundogan, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai, v\u00e0 Fernandinho.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/vlcsnap-2018-04-09-14h55m09s758.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u1ed1 \u00fd, khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c fan Man City t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn. \"T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch Man City nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng h\u1ed5 h\u1eb9n khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o ph\u00f9 hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, th\u1eadt s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c\", m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Twitter b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn. \"V\u1eeba nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y Herrera kh\u1ea1c nh\u1ed5 v\u00e0o logo City. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5. C\u1ea7n c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t anh n\u00e0y\", m\u1ed9t C\u0110V b\u1ee9c x\u00fac. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n c\u1ee7a MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Herrera kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh. \"Ander xem l\u1ea1i video s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ecb s\u1ec9 nh\u1ee5c v\u00ec b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch l\u00e0m th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecnh c\u1edd, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3\". Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c fan MU l\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i Herrera, k\u00eau g\u1ecdi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00f9 h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a anh v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh hay h\u1eefu \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 Herrera nh\u1ed5 n\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ecdt v\u00e0o logo c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n khi \u0111ang ra ngh\u1ec9. H\u00e3y gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi anh ch\u00e0ng n\u00e0y ngay\", m\u1ed9t C\u0110V \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ebft. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi \"b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1eddi\", c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ca ng\u1ee3i Herrera l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng th\u1eadt s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb Man City d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU v\u00f9ng l\u00ean trong hi\u1ec7p hai, t\u1ea1o ra cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c 3-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Etihad c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1edbi ba \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m ch\u1eadm ng\u00e0y \u0111\u0103ng quang c\u1ee7a Man City ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ng\u0103n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y khi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"969","checkdouble":"183883"},{"date":"15:18 09/04","title":"Sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1 s\u1ea3n","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/sai-lam-cua-crystal-palace-khien-cau-thu-doi-nha-phai-pha-san.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"968","checkdouble":"183884"},{"date":"15:24 09/04","title":"B\u00ed \u1ea9n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/9/bi-an-ve-the-luc-sung-man-cua-ronaldo-o-tuoi-33.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color: