4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 18 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf La Liga, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra ngh\u1ec9. Nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 HLV Zidane xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Isco voi gia khong tuong hinh anh\" title=\"Juventus mua Isco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/8/Juventus-mua-Isco-voi-gia-khong-tuong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Isco \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nZidane kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed anh c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng khi b\u1ecb thay ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Isco v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Los Blancos c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-mua-tien-ve-isco-co-buoc-tien-lon-172-183117.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Man City quan t\u00e2m Isco</strong></span>, HLV Pep Guardiola \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Etihad. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh Manchester th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1ebfn 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Isco</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mua Isco \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Man City ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng. Theo Don Balon, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" title=\"Isco the hien phong do tam thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Real-Madrid-ban-tien-ve-Isco-trong-mua-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mua Isco \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Juventus \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Isco nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh, BL\u0110 Juventus \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Isco th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u1ede Etihad, s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi v\u1eady Isco ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/103417-42556/033100\" target=\"_blank\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"966","checkdouble":"183878"},{"date":"14:08 09/04","title":"Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho trung v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/7/ban-ky-luat-vff-ra-an-phat-cho-trung-ve-tang-tien-cua-hagl.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-color:#f7f7f7;border:solid 1px #069241}.articlerelate{padding:6px;display:list-item;list-style-type:square;margin-left:1.2em;border-bottom:dashed 1px #888}.articlerelate:last-child{border-bottom:0}div.articlerelate>a{color:#000;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}div.articlerelate>a:hover{color:#f00;text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold}.articlerelate2{padding:6