=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/1/hlv-slna-trao-co-hoi-cho-cac-cau-thu-tre-tai-afc-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV SLNA trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ea1i AFC Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p Tampines Rovers, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 2-0 ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Singapore.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a SLNA cho bi\u1ebft do l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKhi tham d\u1ef1 AFC Cup 2018, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong hay ti\u1ebfn xa, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 5 V.League.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u00e1ng 4 n\u00e0y, l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a SLNA r\u1ea5t d\u00e0y, trung b\u00ecnh 4 ng\u00e0y/tr\u1eadn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh to\u00e1n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho V.League, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai\", \u00f4ng \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Tampines Rovers c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho SLNA tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Vinh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"964","checkdouble":"183875"},{"date":"22:40 09/04","title":"HLV HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/10/hlv-hagl-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-tung-bung-50-truoc-quang-ninh.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0