lerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV HAGL D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u 9/4, CLB HAGL v\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span> t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Cup Qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL 5-0 Than Quang Ninh HLV HAGL noi gi sau chien thang truoc  hinh anh\" title=\"HAGL 5-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh HLV HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/10/hlv-hagl-che-mat-san-lach-tray-sau-tran-hoa-hai-phong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn\u00a0HAGL 5-0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, V\u0103n To\u00e0n m\u1edf \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Pleiku sau pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhanh \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 1. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Romario v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/5-diem-nhan-dang-chu-y-sau-tran-ha-noi-50-hagl-168-183601.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i </span>t\u1ea1i V-League. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1c pha b\u00f3ng d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTo\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n tri\u1ec7t t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00e1c em \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi l\u00ean, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng\u201d, \u00f4ng Ninh nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/clb-hagl-thu-bon-tien-truoc-khi-vleague-2018-khoi-tranh-168-181378.html\" target=\"_blank\">HAGL</span> c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi ngo\u1ea1i binh Romario Gordon \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho CLB khi hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng Ninh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Jamaica \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 pha t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Romario c\u00f2n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u r\u1ea5t m\u1eebng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa l\u1ed9t x\u00e1c \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"963","checkdouble":"183900"},{"date":"22:58 09/04","title":"HLV Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i v\u1ec1