City nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb U18 v\u00e0 U21.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City vs Liverpool Karius khong cam xuc ngay ve Etihad hinh anh\" title=\"Man City vs Liverpool Karius kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Etihad h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/9/Duoc-Klopp-tin-tuong,-Loris-Karius-noi-ve-Simon-Mignolet-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Loris Karius tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Man City vs Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y v\u1ec1 Etihad, n\u01a1i anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edf h\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 10 n\u0103m v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1eafng 3-0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn trong tay hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Anh n\u00f3i: <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u00f3i chung \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m qu\u00fd b\u00e1u, d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00f4i quen bi\u1ebft \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y, bao g\u1ed3m nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch trang ph\u1ee5c, hai b\u00e1c s\u0129 v\u1eadt l\u00fd tr\u1ecb li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Brian Kidd. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec CLB \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed5i thay r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi Pep Guardiola.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Liverpool l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Man City. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 v\u1eady th\u00f4i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t g\u00ec v\u1edbi Man City hay c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"959","checkdouble":"183904"},{"date":"06:21 10/04","title":"Sao Man City t\u1ed1 Liverpool s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/sao-man-city-to-liverpool-su-dung-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;fo